name: #00011 210911 Nanny Debs on holiday
description: Item #00011 "Nanny Debs on holiday" was drawn on 11th September 2021 by Iris. She was drawing a picture of her nanny and an airplane (in blue) as we are visiting them soon (Spain). It's much clearer to see her figures starting to resemble people and features such as eyes, nose, and mouth. This is NFT number 11 released by the Youngest Artist in the NFT World, Iris. Age at release - 3 years old.
